            <div class="SCXW201944831 BCX8">
<div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW201944831 BCX8">&nbsp;</div>
<div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW201944831 BCX8" style="text-align: justify;">
<p class="Paragraph SCXW201944831 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW201944831 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW201944831 BCX8">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Compreender teorias de inova&ccedil;&atilde;o pode ser fundamental para desenvolver ideias que realmente saiam do papel. Uma dessas teorias &eacute; o </span><span class="NormalTextRun SpellingErrorV2Themed SCXW201944831 BCX8">Decoupling</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW201944831 BCX8">. &Eacute; essencial entender como startups (ou ideias inovadoras) podem substituir empresas consolidadas no mercado. Boa leitura!</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW201944831 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></p>
</div>
<div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW201944831 BCX8" style="text-align: justify;">
<p class="Paragraph SCXW201944831 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW201944831 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW201944831 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW74645405 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW74645405 BCX8">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></span>Voc&ecirc; j&aacute; ouviu falar em </span><span class="NormalTextRun SpellingErrorV2Themed SCXW201944831 BCX8">Decoupling</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW201944831 BCX8"> ou </span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW201944831 BCX8">&ldquo;</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW201944831 BCX8">Cadeia de </span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW201944831 BCX8">v</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW201944831 BCX8">alor do </span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW201944831 BCX8">c</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW201944831 BCX8">liente</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW201944831 BCX8">&rdquo;</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW201944831 BCX8">? Esses conceitos s&atilde;o centrais na teoria criada por Thales Teixeira, professor da </span><span class="NormalTextRun SpellingErrorV2Themed SCXW201944831 BCX8">University</span> <span class="NormalTextRun SpellingErrorV2Themed SCXW201944831 BCX8">of</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW201944831 BCX8"> California e consultor na Decoupling.co, que explica a inova&ccedil;&atilde;o disruptiva em modelos de neg&oacute;cios. No livro "Desvendando a </span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW201944831 BCX8">c</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW201944831 BCX8">adeia de </span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW201944831 BCX8">v</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW201944831 BCX8">alor", Thales mostra como startups podem iniciar uma </span><span class="NormalTextRun SpellingErrorV2Themed SCXW201944831 BCX8">disrup&ccedil;&atilde;o</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW201944831 BCX8"> e como empresas estabelecidas podem responder a isso.</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW201944831 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></p>
</div>
<div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW201944831 BCX8" style="text-align: justify;">
<h3 class="Paragraph SCXW201944831 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW201944831 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW201944831 BCX8">O que &eacute; </span><span class="NormalTextRun SpellingErrorV2Themed SCXW201944831 BCX8">Decoupling</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW201944831 BCX8">?</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW201944831 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></h3>
</div>
<div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW201944831 BCX8" style="text-align: justify;">
<p class="Paragraph SCXW201944831 BCX8" style="text-align: center;"><strong><em><span class="TextRun SCXW201944831 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SpellingErrorV2Themed SCXW201944831 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW74645405 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW74645405 BCX8">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;"</span></span>Decoupling</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW201944831 BCX8"> &eacute; a separa&ccedil;&atilde;o das atividades de valor do consumidor que eram tradicionalmente oferecidas em conjunto." </span></span></em></strong></p>
<p class="Paragraph SCXW201944831 BCX8" style="text-align: left;"><span class="TextRun SCXW201944831 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW201944831 BCX8">Ap&oacute;s v&aacute;rias entrevistas com executivos e visitas a startups, Thales concluiu:</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW201944831 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></p>
</div>
<div class="ListContainerWrapper SCXW201944831 BCX8" style="text-align: justify;">
<ol class="NumberListStyle1 SCXW201944831 BCX8" role="list" start="1">
<li class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW201944831 BCX8" role="listitem" data-leveltext="%1." data-font="" data-listid="22" data-list-defn-props="{" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1">
<p class="Paragraph SCXW201944831 BCX8"><strong><span class="TextRun SCXW201944831 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW201944831 BCX8">A maioria das </span><span class="NormalTextRun SpellingErrorV2Themed SCXW201944831 BCX8">disrup&ccedil;&otilde;es</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW201944831 BCX8"> n&atilde;o &eacute; gerada por novas tecnologias, mas pelos consumidores.</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW201944831 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></strong></p>
</li>
</ol>
</div>
<div class="ListContainerWrapper SCXW201944831 BCX8" style="text-align: justify;">
<ol class="NumberListStyle1 SCXW201944831 BCX8" role="list" start="2">
<li class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW201944831 BCX8" style="font-weight: bold;" role="listitem" data-leveltext="%1." data-font="" data-listid="22" data-list-defn-props="{" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="2" data-aria-level="1">
<p class="Paragraph SCXW201944831 BCX8"><strong><span class="TextRun SCXW201944831 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW201944831 BCX8">Muitas startups identificam o que os clientes desejam e se concentram em etapas espec&iacute;ficas da cadeia de valor para oferecer produtos e servi&ccedil;os melhores.</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW201944831 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></strong></p>
</li>
</ol>
</div>
<div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW201944831 BCX8" style="text-align: justify;">
<p class="Paragraph SCXW201944831 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW201944831 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW201944831 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW74645405 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW74645405 BCX8">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></span>Assim, muitas vezes a resposta &agrave; </span><span class="NormalTextRun SpellingErrorV2Themed SCXW201944831 BCX8">disrup&ccedil;&atilde;o</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW201944831 BCX8"> n&atilde;o &eacute; uma tecnologia inovadora, mas um novo modelo de neg&oacute;cio.</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW201944831 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></p>
</div>
<div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW201944831 BCX8" style="text-align: justify;">
<h3 class="Paragraph SCXW201944831 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW201944831 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW201944831 BCX8">Exemplos de </span><span class="NormalTextRun SpellingErrorV2Themed SCXW201944831 BCX8">Decoupling</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW201944831 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></h3>
</div>
<div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW201944831 BCX8" style="text-align: justify;">
<p class="Paragraph SCXW201944831 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW201944831 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW201944831 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW74645405 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW74645405 BCX8">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></span>O </span><span class="NormalTextRun SpellingErrorV2Themed SCXW201944831 BCX8">Decoupling</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW201944831 BCX8"> pode ser explicado por etapas que um consumidor deseja realizar. Por exemplo, almo&ccedil;ar em um restaurante geralmente envolve sete etapas: escolha, reserva, deslocamento, aloca&ccedil;&atilde;o, pedido, refei&ccedil;&atilde;o e pagamento. Essas etapas podem ser categorizadas como Criadoras de Valor, Cobradoras de Valor ou </span><span class="NormalTextRun SpellingErrorV2Themed SCXW201944831 BCX8">Desgastadoras</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW201944831 BCX8"> de Valor.</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW201944831 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></p>
</div>
<div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW201944831 BCX8" style="text-align: justify;">
<p class="Paragraph SCXW201944831 BCX8"><span class="EOP SCXW201944831 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span><span class="EOP SCXW201944831 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;<strong><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="https://inventta.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Prancheta-1-1-6-1024x268.png" width="783" height="205"></strong></span></p>
</div>
<div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW201944831 BCX8" style="text-align: justify;">
<p class="Paragraph SCXW201944831 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW201944831 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW201944831 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW74645405 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW74645405 BCX8"><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="https://inventta.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Prancheta-1-copia-1-1-1024x311.png" width="761" height="231"> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; </span></span></span></span><span class="TextRun SCXW201944831 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW201944831 BCX8"><em><span class="notion-enable-hover" data-token-index="0"><strong>Observa&ccedil;&atilde;o:</strong>&nbsp;Uma pessoa que gosta de dirigir pode considerar a etapa de deslocamento como Criadora de Valor. Aqui estamos trazendo um exemplo gen&eacute;rico. Quem &ldquo;categoriza&rdquo; a etapa &eacute; o pr&oacute;prio consumidor.</span></em></span></span></p>
<p class="Paragraph SCXW201944831 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW201944831 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW201944831 BCX8">As startups "desacoplam" uma dessas etapas, oferecendo um novo produto ou servi&ccedil;o focado exclusivamente nela. </span></span><span class="EOP SCXW201944831 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{"><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="https://inventta.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Prancheta-3-2-1-1024x513.png" width="611" height="306"></span></p>
</div>
<div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW201944831 BCX8" style="text-align: justify;">
<div class="ListContainerWrapper SCXW201944831 BCX8" style="text-align: justify;">
<ul class="BulletListStyle1 SCXW201944831 BCX8" role="list">
<li class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW201944831 BCX8" role="listitem" data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="23" data-list-defn-props="{" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1">
<p class="Paragraph SCXW201944831 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW201944831 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW201944831 BCX8">TripAdvisor</span></span><span class="TextRun SCXW201944831 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW201944831 BCX8">: Avalia&ccedil;&otilde;es que ajudam na escolha do restaurante.</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW201944831 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></p>
</li>
</ul>
</div>
<div class="ListContainerWrapper SCXW201944831 BCX8" style="text-align: justify;">
<ul class="BulletListStyle1 SCXW201944831 BCX8" role="list">
<li class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW201944831 BCX8" role="listitem" data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="23" data-list-defn-props="{" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="2" data-aria-level="1">
<p class="Paragraph SCXW201944831 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW201944831 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SpellingErrorV2Themed SCXW201944831 BCX8">OpenTable</span></span><span class="TextRun SCXW201944831 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW201944831 BCX8">: Reserva de mesas online.</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW201944831 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></p>
</li>
</ul>
</div>
<div class="ListContainerWrapper SCXW201944831 BCX8" style="text-align: justify;">
<ul class="BulletListStyle1 SCXW201944831 BCX8" role="list">
<li class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW201944831 BCX8" role="listitem" data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="23" data-list-defn-props="{" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="3" data-aria-level="1">
<p class="Paragraph SCXW201944831 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW201944831 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW201944831 BCX8">Uber</span></span><span class="TextRun SCXW201944831 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW201944831 BCX8">: Servi&ccedil;o de transporte.</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW201944831 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></p>
</li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>
<div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW201944831 BCX8" style="text-align: justify;">
<p class="Paragraph SCXW201944831 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW201944831 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW201944831 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW74645405 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW74645405 BCX8">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></span>Essas startups desacoplaram etapas </span><span class="NormalTextRun SpellingErrorV2Themed SCXW201944831 BCX8">desgastadoras</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW201944831 BCX8"> da etapa criadora de valor (comer), tornando-as menos inc&ocirc;modas. Chamamos isso de <strong>"</strong></span></span><strong><span class="TextRun SCXW201944831 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SpellingErrorV2Themed SCXW201944831 BCX8">Decoupling</span></span></strong><span class="TextRun SCXW201944831 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><strong> <span class="NormalTextRun SpellingErrorV2Themed SCXW201944831 BCX8">Desgastador</span></strong><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW201944831 BCX8"><strong> de Valor"</strong>.</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW201944831 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="SCXW201944831 BCX8">
<div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW201944831 BCX8" style="text-align: justify;">
<h3 class="Paragraph SCXW201944831 BCX8">Outros Tipos</h3>
</div>
<div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW201944831 BCX8" style="text-align: justify;">
<p class="Paragraph SCXW201944831 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW201944831 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW201944831 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW74645405 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW74645405 BCX8">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></span>Al&eacute;m do desacoplamento </span><span class="NormalTextRun SpellingErrorV2Themed SCXW201944831 BCX8">desgastador</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW201944831 BCX8"> de valor, existem outros dois tipos:</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW201944831 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></p>
</div>
<div class="ListContainerWrapper SCXW201944831 BCX8" style="text-align: justify;">
<ol class="NumberListStyle1 SCXW201944831 BCX8" role="list" start="1">
<li class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW201944831 BCX8" role="listitem" data-leveltext="%1." data-font="" data-listid="24" data-list-defn-props="{" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1">
<p class="Paragraph SCXW201944831 BCX8"><strong><span class="TextRun SCXW201944831 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SpellingErrorV2Themed SCXW201944831 BCX8">Decoupling</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW201944831 BCX8"> Cobrador de Valor</span></span></strong><span class="TextRun SCXW201944831 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW201944831 BCX8"><strong>:</strong> Uma startup desacopla uma etapa que cobra valor da que cria valor. Por exemplo, a </span><span class="NormalTextRun SpellingErrorV2Themed SCXW201944831 BCX8">SuperCell</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW201944831 BCX8">, com seus jogos </span><span class="NormalTextRun SpellingErrorV2Themed SCXW201944831 BCX8">freemium</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW201944831 BCX8">, desacoplou a compra do jogo da etapa de jogar.</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW201944831 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></p>
</li>
</ol>
</div>
<div class="ListContainerWrapper SCXW201944831 BCX8" style="text-align: justify;">
<ol class="NumberListStyle1 SCXW201944831 BCX8" role="list" start="2">
<li class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW201944831 BCX8" role="listitem" data-leveltext="%1." data-font="" data-listid="24" data-list-defn-props="{" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="2" data-aria-level="1">
<p class="Paragraph SCXW201944831 BCX8"><strong><span class="TextRun SCXW201944831 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SpellingErrorV2Themed SCXW201944831 BCX8">Decoupling</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW201944831 BCX8"> Criador de Valor</span></span></strong><span class="TextRun SCXW201944831 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW201944831 BCX8"><strong>:</strong> Uma startup desacopla uma etapa criadora de valor de outra similar. A </span><span class="NormalTextRun SpellingErrorV2Themed SCXW201944831 BCX8">Twitch</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW201944831 BCX8">, por exemplo, criou um modelo de neg&oacute;cio focado em transmiss&otilde;es de jogos online, percebendo que consumidores gostam de assistir a jogos tanto quanto de jog&aacute;-los.</span></span> <span class="EOP SCXW201944831 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></p>
</li>
</ol>
</div>
<div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW201944831 BCX8"><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="https://inventta.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Prancheta-3-copia-3-2-1024x513.png" width="768" height="385"></div>
<div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW201944831 BCX8" style="text-align: justify;">
<p class="Paragraph SCXW201944831 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW201944831 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW201944831 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW74645405 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW74645405 BCX8">&nbsp;O que diferencia os tipos de <span class="notion-enable-hover" data-token-index="1">Decoupling</span>&nbsp;&eacute; a&nbsp;<span class="notion-enable-hover" data-token-index="3">categoria da etapa que est&aacute; sendo desacoplada</span>, como podemos ver no resumo a seguir:<strong> </strong></span></span></span></span></p>
<p class="Paragraph SCXW201944831 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW201944831 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW201944831 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW74645405 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW74645405 BCX8"><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="https://inventta.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Prancheta-3-copia-2-4-1024x563.png" width="684" height="376"></span></span></span></span></p>
<h3 class="Paragraph SCXW201944831 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW201944831 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW201944831 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW74645405 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW74645405 BCX8"><strong>&nbsp;</strong></span></span><strong>Case: Best </strong></span><strong><span class="NormalTextRun SpellingErrorV2Themed SCXW201944831 BCX8">Buy</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW201944831 BCX8"> vs. </span><span class="NormalTextRun SpellingErrorV2Themed SCXW201944831 BCX8">Amazon</span></strong></span><strong><span class="EOP SCXW201944831 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></strong></h3>
</div>
<div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW201944831 BCX8" style="text-align: justify;">
<p class="Paragraph SCXW201944831 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW201944831 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW201944831 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW74645405 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW74645405 BCX8">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></span>Um exemplo de impacto do </span><span class="NormalTextRun SpellingErrorV2Themed SCXW201944831 BCX8">decoupling</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW201944831 BCX8"> &eacute; o caso da Best </span><span class="NormalTextRun SpellingErrorV2Themed SCXW201944831 BCX8">Buy</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW201944831 BCX8"> e da </span><span class="NormalTextRun SpellingErrorV2Themed SCXW201944831 BCX8">Amazon</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW201944831 BCX8">. Em 2012, a Best </span><span class="NormalTextRun SpellingErrorV2Themed SCXW201944831 BCX8">Buy</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW201944831 BCX8"> come&ccedil;ou a perder vendas devido ao </span><span class="NormalTextRun SpellingErrorV2Themed SCXW201944831 BCX8">showrooming</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW201944831 BCX8">, onde consumidores visitavam lojas f&iacute;sicas para ver produtos, mas compravam online por pre&ccedil;os mais baixos. A </span><span class="NormalTextRun SpellingErrorV2Themed SCXW201944831 BCX8">Amazon</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW201944831 BCX8"> desacoplou a visita &agrave; loja f&iacute;sica (n&atilde;o gera valor) da compra do produto (gera valor).</span></span></p>
<h4 class="Paragraph SCXW201944831 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW201944831 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW201944831 BCX8">A Resposta da Best&nbsp;</span><span class="NormalTextRun SpellingErrorV2Themed SCXW201944831 BCX8">Buy</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW201944831 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></h4>
</div>
<div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW201944831 BCX8" style="text-align: justify;">
<p class="Paragraph SCXW201944831 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW201944831 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW201944831 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW74645405 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW74645405 BCX8">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></span>A Best </span><span class="NormalTextRun SpellingErrorV2Themed SCXW201944831 BCX8">Buy</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW201944831 BCX8"> inicialmente tentou combater o </span><span class="NormalTextRun SpellingErrorV2Themed SCXW201944831 BCX8">showrooming</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW201944831 BCX8"> com v&aacute;rias estrat&eacute;gias, como remover c&oacute;digos de barras dos produtos e criar um app pr&oacute;prio, mas sem sucesso. Foi s&oacute; depois de meses, com uma nova gest&atilde;o, que a empresa decidiu entender e se adaptar ao novo comportamento dos consumidores. Eles come&ccedil;aram a cobrar das grandes empresas para exibir seus produtos de forma mais profissional e personalizada dentro das lojas, incentivando o </span><span class="NormalTextRun SpellingErrorV2Themed SCXW201944831 BCX8">showrooming</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW201944831 BCX8"> e gerando receita sem prejudicar o cliente final.</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW201944831 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="Paragraph SCXW201944831 BCX8"><span class="EOP SCXW201944831 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{"><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="https://inventta.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Untitled-1024x588.png" width="773" height="444"></span></p>
</div>
<div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW201944831 BCX8" style="text-align: justify;">
<p class="Paragraph SCXW201944831 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW201944831 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW201944831 BCX8"><span class="TextRun SCXW74645405 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW74645405 BCX8">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></span>Este exemplo mostra como empresas estabelecidas podem se adaptar ao </span><span class="NormalTextRun SpellingErrorV2Themed SCXW201944831 BCX8">decoupling</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW201944831 BCX8">. No entanto, muitas empresas ainda est&atilde;o vulner&aacute;veis e podem sofrer consequ&ecirc;ncias se n&atilde;o entenderem o que seus consumidores realmente querem e como seus comportamentos est&atilde;o mudando.</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW201944831 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></p>
</div>
<div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW201944831 BCX8">
<p class="Paragraph SCXW201944831 BCX8" style="text-align: justify;"><span class="TextRun SCXW201944831 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW201944831 BCX8">Agora que voc&ecirc; entendeu a teoria do </span><span class="NormalTextRun SpellingErrorV2Themed SCXW201944831 BCX8">decoupling</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW201944831 BCX8">, que tal compartilhar uma ideia inovadora no </span><span class="NormalTextRun SpellingErrorV2Themed SCXW201944831 BCX8">Avantt.i</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW201944831 BCX8"> que "desacople" alguma etapa da cadeia de valor dos seus clientes? N&atilde;o se esque&ccedil;a de criar uma proposta de valor clara e significativa para a mudan&ccedil;a proposta. At&eacute; a pr&oacute;xima!</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW201944831 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;<br></span></p>
<hr>
<h3>Sobre a Avantt.i&nbsp;</h3>
<p><span class="TextRun SCXW195930854 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW195930854 BCX8">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></span>A Avantt.i &eacute; uma plataforma de inova&ccedil;&atilde;o desenvolvida pela Inventta, para gestores de inova&ccedil;&atilde;o e gerentes de projeto.</p>
<p><span class="TextRun SCXW195930854 BCX8" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW195930854 BCX8">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></span>Com m&oacute;dulos de intra, open e gest&atilde;o do portf&oacute;lio, oferecemos uma vis&atilde;o completa da Gest&atilde;o da Inova&ccedil;&atilde;o para alavancar suas iniciativas.</p>
<ul>
<li><strong>Vis&atilde;o global e gest&atilde;o do portf&oacute;lio: </strong>Atrav&eacute;s da consolida&ccedil;&atilde;o do portf&oacute;lio de inova&ccedil;&atilde;o, a Avantt.i ajuda a identificar os principais projetos e avan&ccedil;ar com assertividade. Tudo em uma &uacute;nica plataforma.&nbsp;</li>
<li><strong>Programa de intra: </strong>Crie desafios e obtenha participa&ccedil;&atilde;o dos colaboradores. A inova&ccedil;&atilde;o vira rotina e voc&ecirc; impulsiona a cultura de inova&ccedil;&atilde;o na empresa.</li>
<li><strong>Open Innovation:</strong> Chame startups e parceiros para desafios, gerencie parceria na plataforma e tenha acesso a mais de 23.000 startups na nossa base.</li>
<li><strong>M&eacute;tricas Acion&aacute;veis: </strong>Influencie a organiza&ccedil;&atilde;o a investir em esfor&ccedil;os de inova&ccedil;&atilde;o com base em m&eacute;tricas claras e acion&aacute;veis. Me&ccedil;a resultados dos projetos e comunique o sucesso das iniciativas</li>
<li><strong>Inova&ccedil;&atilde;o Integrada e Transparente: </strong>Gerencie projetos de diferentes esteiras e horizontes, com colabora&ccedil;&atilde;o de parceiros e equipe, visualizando o portf&oacute;lio globalmente.&nbsp;&nbsp;</li>
<li style="text-align: left;"><strong>Engajamento com Conhecimento: </strong>Transforme a inova&ccedil;&atilde;o em h&aacute;bito com trilhas de conhecimento e mentorias dispon&iacute;veis ao longo da jornada.&nbsp;<br><br>Conhe&ccedil;a <a href="https://materiais.avanttinovacao.com.br/avantti-inovacao-primeiro-passo">aqui</a>, solicite uma demonstra&ccedil;&atilde;o guiada e teste gr&aacute;tis.<a href="https://materiais.avanttinovacao.com.br/avantti-inovacao-primeiro-passo"><span class="EOP SCXW195930854 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{"><img src="https://d335luupugsy2.cloudfront.net/cms/files/808420/1720784635/$63vucuqtfj9" width="673" height="448"></span></a></li>
</ul>
<p class="Paragraph SCXW201944831 BCX8" style="text-align: justify;"><span class="EOP SCXW201944831 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{">&nbsp;</span></p>
</div>
